20the%20No.%209%20spot%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22MS%20Dhoni%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F700-ms-dhoni-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMS%20Dhoni%3C%2Fa%3E%20featured%20as%20a%20No.%207%20batter%20for%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20(CSK)%20in%20the%206-run%20defeat%20against%20Rajasthan%20Royals%20(RR)%20on%20Sunday.%20The%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202025%20has%20seen%20Dhoni%20bat%20quite%20down%20in%20the%20order%2C%20ranging%20from%20No.%207%20to%20No.%209.%20Having%20already%20produced%20a%20few%20fine%20cameos%20with%20the%20bat%2C%20there%20are%20many%20who%20wonder%20why%20the%20franchise%20isn't%20sending%20Thala%20up%20the%20order%2C%20at%20a%20position%20where%20his%20explosiveness%20can%20benefit%20the%20team%20more.%20After%20the%20defeat%20against%20the%20Royals%2C%20CSK%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Stephen%20Fleming%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F187-stephen-fleming-playerprofile%5C%22%3EStephen%20Fleming%3C%2Fa%3E%20solved%20this%20mystery%2C%20putting%20the%20topic%20to%20bed%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20burning%20topic%20of%20Dhoni's%20batting%20position%2C%20Fleming%20said%20that%20the%20former%20India%20captain's%20knees%20aren't%20what%20they%20used%20to%20be.%20Hence%2C%20it%20is%20not%20feasible%20for%20him%20to%20bat%20for%2010-12%20overs%20in%20match%2C%20considering%20he%20also%20keeps%20wickets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYeah%2C%20it's%20a%20time%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20Fleming%20said%20in%20the%20post-match%20press%20conference.%20%26quot%3BMS%20judges%20it.%20His%20body%20is%2C%20his%20knees%20aren't%20what%20they%20used%20to%20be.%20And%20he's%20moving%20okay%2C%20but%20there's%20still%20an%20attrition%20aspect%20to%20it.%20He%20can't%20bat%2010%20overs%20running%20full%20stick.%20So%20he%20will%20gauge%20on%20the%20day%20what%20he%20can%20give%20us.%20If%20the%20game's%20in%20the%20balance%20like%20today%2C%20he%20will%20go%20a%20little%20bit%20earlier%2C%20and%20he%20backs%20other%20players%20when%20other%20opportunities%20are%20up.%20So%20he's%20balancing%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFleming%20said%20that%20the%20ideal%20time%20for%20Dhoni%20to%20bat%20is%2013th%20or%2014th%20over%20onwards%2C%20that%20too%20depending%20upon%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20said%20it%20last%20year%20%5Bas%20well%5D%2C%20he's%20too%20valuable%20to%20us%20-%20leadership%20and%20wicket-keeping%20-%20to%20throw%20him%20in%20nine%2C%20ten%20overs.%20He%20has%20actually%20never%20done%20that.%20So%2C%20look%2C%20from%20around%2013-14%20overs%2C%20he's%20looking%20to%20go%20depending%20on%20who's%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20comments%20Fleming%20made%20in%20the%20press%20conference%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20Dhoni's%20skills%20as%20a%20leader%20and%20a%20wicket-keeper%20are%20more%20important%20to%20the%20Super%20Kings%20in%20IPL%202025%20than%20what%20he%20brings%20to%20the%20table%20as%20a%20batter.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743388740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fnc39gr9o_ms-dhoni-stairs-bcci_625x300_31_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2025%2Fipl-2025-csk-coach-hits-bullseye-as-he-explains-reason-behind-ms-dhonis-batting-position-8050696%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22MS%20Dhoni%20has%20batted%20as%20low%20as%20No.%209%20in%20the%20ongoing%20IPL%202025%20for%20CSK.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Asked%20About%20CSK's%20Poor%20Form%2C%20Skipper%20Ruturaj%20Gives%20Unfiltered%20Reply%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChennai%20Super%20Kings%20skipper%20Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%20blamed%20their%20poor%20starts%20and%20fielding%20lapses%20as%20key%20reasons%20behind%20their%20six-run%20defeat%20to%20Rajasthan%20Royals%20in%20the%20IPL%20on%20Sunday%2C%20marking%20their%20second%20consecutive%20loss.%20Nitish%20Rana's%20blistering%2036-ball%2081%2C%20combined%20with%20Wanindu%20Hasaranga's%20four-wicket%20haul%2C%20powered%20Rajasthan%20Royals%20to%20a%20hard-fought%20win%20at%20the%20Barsapara%20Stadium.%20Chasing%20183%2C%20CSK%20lost%20Rachin%20Ravindra%20for%20duck%20while%20Rahul%20Tripathi%20got%20out%20after%20the%20power%20play%20as%20they%20finished%20at%20176%2F6.%20They%20had%20lost%20their%20last%20match%20at%20home%20to%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%2C%20a%20first%20in%2017%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20haven't%20been%20getting%20good%20starts%2C%20but%20once%20we%20do%2C%20things%20will%20be%20different%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gaikwad%20admitted%20at%20the%20post-match%20presentation.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20conceded%208-10%20extra%20runs%20through%20misfields%2C%20and%20that's%20something%20we%20need%20to%20improve.%E2%80%9D%20Gaikwad's%20valiant%2063%20anchored%20the%20chase%2C%20but%20with%20wickets%20falling%20at%20regular%20intervals%2C%20CSK%20couldn't%20cross%20the%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20batting%20at%20No.%203%2C%20the%20CSK%20captain%20explained%20that%20it%20was%20a%20pre-planned%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COver%20the%20years%2C%20Ajinkya%20batted%20at%20three%20while%20Rayudu%20handled%20the%20middle%20overs.%20We%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20better%20if%20I%20came%20in%20later%20to%20steady%20things%2C%20while%20Tripathi%20could%20attack%20upfront.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20decided%20at%20the%20auction%2C%20and%20I%20have%20no%20problem%20with%20it.%20Anyway%2C%20I'm%20getting%20to%20bat%20early%20in%20every%20game%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20with%20a%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Rajasthan%20Royals'%20stand-in%20skipper%20Riyan%20Parag%2C%20leading%20in%20his%20hometown%2C%20was%20relieved%20to%20end%20their%20Guwahati%20leg%20with%20a%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20felt%20we%20were%2020%20short.%20We%20were%20going%20well%20in%20the%20middle%20overs%20but%20lost%20a%20couple%20of%20quick%20wickets.%20However%2C%20our%20bowlers%20executed%20our%20plans%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20Parag%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe've%20had%20two%20tough%20games%20--%20one%20where%20we%20conceded%20280%20and%20another%20where%20we%20couldn't%20defend%20180.%20This%20win%20was%20much%20needed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20brilliant%20on%20the%20field%20with%20Parag%20taking%20a%20blinder%20to%20dismiss%20Shivam%20Dube%20for%2018%2C%20while%20Shimron%20Hetmyer's%20splendid%20catch%20ended%20MS%20Dhoni's%20late%20blitz%20for%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFielding%20makes%20up%20for%20the%2020%20runs%20that%20we%20were%20short.%20We%20have%20been%20working%20with%20Dishant%20Yagnik%2C%20our%20fielding%20coach.%20So%20it%20shows%2C%26quot%3B%20Parag%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743388620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F8qr48fkg_c_625x300_31_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2025%2Fhavent-been-getting-ruturaj-gaikwads-honest-verdict-on-csks-loss-against-rr-8049254%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20skipper%20Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%20blamed%20their%20poor%20starts%20and%20fielding%20lapses%20as%20key%20reasons%20behind%20their%20six-run%20defeat%20to%20Rajasthan%20Royals%20in%20the%20IPL.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Billie%20Eilish%20and%20Finneas%20Join%20Jason%20Owen%E2%80%99s%20Sandbox%20Management%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743388353000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FGettyImages-2066791992-e1726590814648.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236352266%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Billie%20Eilish%20and%20her%20brother%