dent%20Vladimir%20Putin%20over%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20US%20news%20network's%20NBC's%20Kristen%20Welker%20in%20an%20early-morning%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fdonald-trump%2Ftrump-angry-putin-zelenskyy-iran-sanctions-rcna198729%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ephone%20call%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Mr%20Trump%20reportedly%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bvery%20angry%2C%20pissed%20off%26quot%3B%20over%20recent%20remarks%20by%20Mr%20Putin%20that%20questioned%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky's%20leadership.%20The%20Russian%20president%20suggested%20that%20Ukraine%20should%20consider%20alternative%20leadership%20as%20part%20of%20a%20potential%20peace%20settlement%20-%20an%20idea%20Mr%20Trump%20dismissed%20as%20counterproductive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Russia%20and%20I%20are%20unable%20to%20make%20a%20deal%20on%20stopping%20the%20bloodshed%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20if%20I%20think%20it%20was%20Russia's%20fault...%20I%20am%20going%20to%20put%20secondary%20tariffs%20on%20all%20oil%20coming%20out%20of%20Russia%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Welker%20quoted%20Mr%20Trump%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trump%2C%20who%20has%20previously%20referred%20to%20Mr%20Zelensky%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bdictator%2C%26quot%3B%20has%20had%20a%20tumultuous%20relationship%20with%20the%20Ukrainian%20president.%20The%20two%20leaders%20clashed%20during%20Mr%20Zelensky's%20recent%20visit%20to%20Washington%2C%20where%20Mr%20Trump%20criticised%20Ukraine's%20wartime%20governance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trump%20reportedly%20claimed%20that%20Mr%20Putin%20was%20aware%20of%20his%20anger%20but%20insisted%20that%20he%20still%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bgood%20relationship%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20Russian%20President.%20Mr%20Trump%20added%20that%20his%20anger%20would%20subside%20if%20Mr%20Putin%20made%20the%20%26quot%3Bright%20decisions%26quot%3B%20regarding%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5