attempts%20to%20incite%20communal%20tension%20over%20Aurangazeb's%20tomb%20and%20said%20history%20shouldn't%20be%20viewed%20from%20the%20prism%20of%20caste%20and%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaj%20Thackeray%20also%20asked%20people%20not%20to%20rely%20on%20WhatsApp%20forwards%20for%20historical%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20his%20annual%20Gudhi%20Padwa%20rally%20at%20Shivaji%20Park%20here%2C%20Raj%C2%A0Thackeray%20said%20the%20Mughal%20ruler%20wanted%20to%20%26quot%3Bkill%20a%20thought%20called%20Shivaji%26quot%3B%20but%20failed%20and%20died%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfzal%20Khan%2C%20the%20Bijapur%20general%2C%20was%20buried%20near%20the%20Pratapgadh%20Fort%20and%20it%20couldn't%20have%20been%20done%20without%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj's%20permission%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaj%C2%A0Thackeray's%20comments%20came%20amid%20demands%20by%20right-wing%20outfits%20for%20the%20removal%20of%20Aurangzeb's%20tomb%20located%20in%20Chhatrapati%20Sambhajinagar%20district.%20Protests%20over%20the%20issue%20had%20also%20triggered%20violence%20in%20Nagpur%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20we%20want%20to%20let%20the%20world%20know%20that%20these%20people%20sought%20to%20destroy%20the%20Marathas%20but%20were%20wiped%20out%20instead.%20Stop%20reading%20history%20on%20WhatsApp%20and%20rather%20delve%20into%20history%20books%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUrging%20people%20not%20to%20get%20provoked%20and%20distracted%2C%20he%20said%20that%20socio-political%20situations%20were%20different%20in%20pre-Shivaji%20and%20post-Shivaji%20eras.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20forgotten%20the%20real%20issues%20of%20the%20present%20time.%20Hindus%20who%20feel%20awakened%20after%20a%20movie%20are%20of%20no%20use.%20Did%20you%20learn%20about%20Sambhaji%20Maharaj's%20sacrifice%20because%20of%20Vicky%20Kaushal%20and%20about%20Aurangazeb%20because%20of%20Akshaye%20Khanna%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asked