%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ftabu-supriya-pathak-kajol-celebrating-the-most-iconic-female-villains-of-bollywood%2Farticleshow%2F119764705.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22500-Year-Old%20Telugu%20Rock%20Inscription%20Found%20In%20Telangana's%20Anantgiri%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETelugu%20inscriptions%20dating%20back%20to%201517%20CE%20have%20been%20found%20in%20parts%20of%20Telangana%20by%20the%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India.%20%C2%A0The%20find%20comes%20months%20after%20a%20treasure%20trove%20of%20inscriptions%20and%20rock%20art%20was%20found%20in%20neighbouring%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ASI%20team%20found%20the%20inscriptions%20at%20Narasimhulagutta%2C%20Anantagiri%2C%20Rajanna%20Sircilla%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20the%20inscription%20is%20a%20praise%20of%20various%20local%20Hindu%20gods%2C%20and%20records%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20Vishnu%20temple%20on%20top%20of%20a%20hill%20in%20Anantagiri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20inscriptions%20that%20are%20800%20to%202000%20years%20old%20were%20found%20in%20Lankkamala%20Reserve%20Forest%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20The%20survey%20by%20the%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India%20also%20found%20rock%20art%20thought%20to%20be%20from%20the%20megalithic%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20said%20to%20be%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdeep-in-andhra-forest-treasure-trove-of-rock-paintings-inscriptions-7840448%5C%22%3Ebiggest%20archaeological%20find%20in%20recent%20times%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20led%20to%20the%20discovery%20of%20three%20rock%20shelters.%20One%20of%20these%20contained%20stunning%20prehistoric%20paintings%20depicting%20animals%2C%20geometric%20patterns%2C%20and%20human%20figures%2C%20officials%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paintings%2C%20dating%20back%20to%20the%20Megalithic%20(Iron%20Age)%20and%20early%20historic%20periods%20(2500%20BCE-2nd%20century%20CE)%2C%20were%20created%20using%20natural%20materials%20like%20red%20ochre%2C%20kaolin%2C%20animal%20fat%2C%20and%20crushed%20bones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETelangana%20also%20has%20a%20rich%20heritage%20in%20terms%20of%20rock%20inscriptions%20that%20provide%20glimpses%20of%20its%20history.%20Last%20year%2C%20an%20ASI%20team%20found%20three%20inscriptions%20from%20the%20Chalukya%20period%20in%20Vikarabad's%20Kankal%20village.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20oldest-known%20rock%20inscription%20in%20Telugu%20in%20the%20state%20is%20the%20Keesara%20Gutta%20inscription%2C%20that%20dates%20back%20to%20420%20CE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20the%20Bommalagutta%20inscription%20in%20Karimnagar%20and%20one%20from%20the%209th%20century%20in%20Warangal.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743354720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Firk3lqao_telangana-rock-inscription_625x300_30_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F500-year-old-telugu-rock-inscription-found-in-telanganas-anantgiri-8048816%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Telugu%20inscriptions%20dating%20back%20to%201517%20CE%20have%20been%20found%20in%20parts%20of%20Telangana%20by%20the%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India.%20The%20find%20comes%20months%20after%20a%20treasure%20trove%20of%20inscriptions%20and%20rock%20art%20was%20found%20in%20neighbouring%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F500-year-old-telugu-rock-inscription-found-in-telanganas-anantgiri-8048816%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Brooklyn%20wigmaker%20accused%20of%20killing%20mom%2C%20two%20kids%20in%20horror%20crash%20previously%20won%20%242m%20NYPD%20settlement%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743354715000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A