ndiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Flagaan-iqbal-m-s-dhoni-83-ghoomer-why-cricket-movies-hit-a-spectacular-shot-with-audiences%2Farticleshow%2F119762637.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manisha%E2%80%99s%20old%20video%20on%20Nepal%20as%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20nation%E2%80%99%20resurfaces%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743350106000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-119763141%2Cimgsize-27144.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fmanisha-koiralas-video-calling-nepal-the-only-hindu-nation-in-the-world-resurfaces-online-netizens-ask-then-why-did-she-come-to-india%2Farticleshow%2F119763053.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F119763053.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EVeteran%20actress%20Manisha%20Koirala%20has%20once%20again%20found%20herself%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20heated%20discussion.%20The%20actress%2C%20who%20hails%20from%20Nepal%20and%20made%20a%20name%20for%20herself%20in%20Hindi%20cinema%20with%20her%20debut%20in%20'Saudagar'%20(1991)%2C%20has%20recently%20been%20the%20subject%20of%20renewed%20attention.%20A%20video%20of%20the%20Heeramandi%20actress%20speaking%20about%20Nepal%E2%80%99s%20past%20as%20a%20Hindu%20nation%20in%20an%20old%20interview%20has%20resurfaced%20online.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fmanisha-koiralas-video-calling-nepal-the-only-hindu-nation-in-the-world-resurfaces-online-netizens-ask-then-why-did-she-come-to-india%2Farticleshow%2F119763053.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Centre%20To%20Convert%20Vodafone%20Idea%20Spectrum%20Dues%20Worth%20Rs%2036%2C950%20Crore%20Into%20Equity%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVodafone's%20spectrum%20auction%20dues%20worth%20Rs%2036%2C950%20crore%20will%20be%20converted%20into%20equity%20by%20the%20government%2C%20which%20will%20increase%20its%20holding%20in%20Vodafone%20Idea%20to%2048.99%20per%20cent%20-%20up%20from%2022.6%20per%20cent.%C2%A0The%20government%20has%20been%20the%20single-largest%20shareholder%20in%20the%20debt-ridden%20Vodafone%20Idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20it%20will%20receive%203%2C695%20shares%20at%20issue%20price%20of%20Rs%2010%20a%20share%2C%20the%20company%20said%20in%20a%20regulatory%20filing%20on%20Sunday.%C2%A0The%20shares%20to%20be%20issued%20within%2030%20days%20of%20the%20order.%20The%20move%20is%20in%20line%20with%20the%20relief%20package%20announced%20for%20the%20telecom%20sector%20in%20September%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outstanding%20spectrum%20dues%20include%20deferred%20dues%20repayable%20after%20expiry%20of%20the%20moratorium%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20promoters%20will%20continue%20having%20operational%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Ministry%20of%20Communications...%20in%20line%20with%20the%20September%202021%20Reforms%20and%20Support%20Package%20for%20Telecom%20Sector%20has%20decided%20to%20convert%20the%20outstanding%20spectrum%20auction%20dues%2C%20including%20deferred%20dues%20repayable%20after%20expiry%20of%20the%20moratorium%20period%2C%20into%20equity%20shares%20to%20be%20issued%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%20The%20total%20amount%20to%20be%20converted%20into%20equity%20shares%20is%20Rs%2036%2C950%20crore%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20filing%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPost%20the%20aforesaid%20issuance%20of%20equity%20shares%2C%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20shareholding%20in%20the%20Company%20will%20increase%20from%20existing%2022.60%20per%20cent%20to%20approximately%2048.99%20per%20cent.%20The%20promoters%20will%20continue%20to%20have%20operational%20control%20of%20the%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20filing%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Vodafone%20Idea%20CEO%20Akshaya%20Moondra%20had%20written%20to%20the%20telecom%20department%20asking%20for%20approval%20of%20equity%20conversion%20for%20the%20spectrum%20auction%20dues%20and%20Adjusted%20Gross%20Revenue%20from%202012%20to%202016%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2Fuae%2Fhome-away-from-home-why-indian-startups-are-flocking-to-dubais-free-zones%2Farticleshow%2F119103839.cms%5C%22%3Ereported%20Economic%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20report%20said%20the%20letter%20outlines%20Vodafone-Idea's%20inability%20to%20pay%20%C2%A0Rs%205%2C431%20crore%20in%20cash%20or%20provide%20a%20bank%20guarantee%20for%20the%20shortfall%20for%20the%202015%20spectrum%20auction.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743349320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fp5da23no_vodafone-idea_650x400_30_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgovernment-to-raise-stake-in-vodafone-idea-to-48-99-with-acquisition-of-shares-worth-rs-36-950-crore-8048014%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Vodafone's%20spectrum%20auction%20dues%20worth%20Rs%2036%2C950%20crore%20will%20be%20converted%20into%20equity%20by%20the%20government%2C%20which%20will%20increase%20its%20holding%20in%20Vodafone%20Idea%20to%2048.99%20per%20cent%20-%20up%20from%2022.6%20per%20cent.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgovernment-to-raise-stake-in-vodafone-idea-to-48-99-with-acquisition-of-shares-worth-rs-36-950-crore-8048014%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IIIT%20Allahabad%20Student%20Dies%20By%20Suicide%20In%20Hostel%20A%20Day%20Before%20Birthday%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20first-year%20student%20of%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Information%20Technology%20(IIIT)%2C%20Allahabad%2C%20allegedly%20died%20by%20suicide%20at%20the%20hostel%20campus%20on%20Saturday%20night%2C%20police%20said%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20in%20Jhalwa%20area%20of%20Prayagraj%20took%20place%20just%20a%20day%20before%20the%20specially-abled%20student%20from%20Telangana%2C%20Rahul%20Madala%20Chaitanya%2C%20was%20to%20celebrate%20his%2021st%20birthday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20no%20suicide%20note%20was%20recovered%20from%20the%20spot%20but%20a%20preliminary%20probe%20suggested%20that%20Rahul%20was%20upset%20after%20he%20failed%20in%20an%20examination.%20The%20institute%20said%20a%20committee%20has%20been%20formed%20to%20probe%20the%20incident%20and%20directed%20to%20submit%20a%20report%20within%20seven%20days.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%2C%20Rahul%20jumped%20from%20the%20fifth%20floor%20of%20his%20hostel%20at%20the%20IIIT%20campus%20at%20around%2011.55pm%20on%20Saturday.%20%26quot%3BUpon%20receiving%20information%2C%20a%20police%20team%20rushed%20to%20the%20spot%20and%20took%20him%20to%20the%20hospital%20where%20he%20succumbed%20to%20injuries%2C%26quot%3B%20Dhoomanganj%20Assistant%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(ACP)%20Ajendra%20Yadav%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20seemed%20the%20student%20was%20upset%20for%20the%20past%20two%20to%20three%20days%20after%20he%20failed%20to%20clear%20an%20examination%2C%20police%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20a%20detailed%20probe%20is%20underway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERahul's%20Last%20Message%20To%20Mother%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20student's%20family%20arrived%20in%20Prayagraj%20from%20Telangana%20on%20Sunday%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul's%20mother%20Swarnalatha%20said%20she%20last%20heard%20from%20her%20son%20on%20Saturday%20night.%20%26quot%3BHe%20had%20sent%20a%20message%2C%20asking%20me%20to%20take%20care%20of%20his%20younger%20brother%20and%20father%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20got%20scared%20on%20seeing%20the%20message%20and%20called%20him%20but%20his%20phone%20was%20off.%20Then%20I%20called%20his%20friend%20who%20went%20to%20check%20on%20him.%20His%20friend%20asked%20another%20student%20who%20was%20passing%20by%20about%20Rahul's%20whereabouts.%20He%20then%20abruptly%20disconnected%20the%20call.%20He%20called%20me%2010%20minutes%20later%2C%20saying%20my%20son%20is%20being%20taken%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwarnalatha%20said%20she%20learnt%20about%20the%20suicide%20on%20reaching%20the%20campus%20on%20Sunday%20afternoon.%20She%20said%20the%20institute%20informed%20her%20that%20he%20had%20skipped%20classes%20for%20six%20months.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20administration%20never%20informed%20us%20anything%20about%20this%20earlier%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fa4iuftn_iiit-allahabad-student-suicide_625x300_30_March_25.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAIR%20Rank%20Of%2052%20In%20JEE%20Mains%20Under%20EWS%20Category%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20was%20a%20good%20student%20and%20had%20secured%20an%20All%20India%20Rank%20of%2052%20in%20the%20Economically%20Weaker%20Sections%20category%20in%20the%20JEE%20Mains%20exam%20last%20year%2C%20she%20said.%20She%20added%20that%20since%20her%20son%20could%20not%20speak%2C%20he%20would%20often%20video%20call%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul's%20father%20runs%20a%20tiffin%20business%20in%20Telangana.%20The%20student%20was%20the%20elder%20of%20the%20two%20sons.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwarnalatha%20said%20her%20son%20would%20only%20study%2C%20watch%20television%20and%20browse%20his%20phone.%20%26quot%3BHe%20did%20not%20like%20roaming%20aroun