.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FShiv-Kumar-Green-Entrepreneur-LED-bulb-manufacturer-Dadda-Patti-Uttarakhand_11zon-1743077050-768x395.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FShiv-Kumar-Green-Entrepreneur-LED-bulb-manufacturer-Dadda-Patti-Uttarakhand_11zon-1743077050-1536x790.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FShiv-Kumar-Green-Entrepreneur-LED-bulb-manufacturer-Dadda-Patti-Uttarakhand_11zon-1743077050-1200x617.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FShiv-Kumar-Green-Entrepreneur-LED-bulb-manufacturer-Dadda-Patti-Uttarakhand_11zon-1743077050-150x77.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-416328%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22987%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGreen%20entrepreneur%20Shiv%20Kumar%20is%20an%20LED%20bulb%20manufacturer%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20a%20Delhi-based%20social%20enterprise%2C%20%E2%80%98Development%20Alternatives%E2%80%99%2C%20launched%20the%20%E2%80%98Inclusive%20Entrepreneurship%E2%80%99%20programme%20with%20one%20big%20idea%20%E2%80%94%20turning%20job%20seekers%20into%20job%20creators.%20Instead%20of%20focusing%20solely%20on%20providing%20jobs%2C%20the%20programme%20set%20out%20to%20build%20entrepreneurial%20ecosystems%20%E2%80%94%20support%20systems%20that%20help%20people%20start%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F113935%2Ffoundation-poor-women-business-owners-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrow%20their%20own%20businesses%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20vision%20aimed%20at%20underserved%20communities%2C%20particularly%20women%20and%20youth%20and%20seeks%20to%20create%20long-term%20economic%20growth%20while%20promoting%20social%20inclusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20unique%20approach%20rooted%20in%20social%20innovation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3