20collaborative%20effort%20between%20NASA%2C%20ESA%2C%20Roscosmos%2C%20Kibo%2C%20and%20the%20Canadian%20Space%20Agency%20(CSA)%2C%20the%20ISS%20has%20been%20home%20to%20astronauts%20for%20over%20two%20decades%2C%20helping%20researchers%20understand%20how%20humans%20can%20survive%20beyond%20Earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20basic%20reason%20for%20having%20the%20space%20station%20is%20to%20understand%20the%20possibilities%20of%20human%20survival%20on%20the%20Moon%20and%20Mars%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Rachna%20Arora%2C%20a%20Physics%20Educator%20at%20Shiv%20Nadar%20School%2C%20Noida.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20also%20helps%20to%20explore%20how%20crops%20can%20be%20grown%20in%20space%20and%20how%20microgravity%20impacts%20human%20biology.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20were%20astronauts%20Butch%20Wilmore%20and%20Sunita%20Williams%20stuck%20in%20space%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAstronauts%20Butch%20Wilmore%20and%20Sunita%20Williams%20embarked%20on%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360476%2Fnasa-space-camp-for-students-astronauts-geet-alabama-us-space-rocket-centre-how-to-get-apply%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeight-day%20mission%3C%2Fa%3E%20aboard%20the%20Boeing%20Starliner%20(CST-100)%2C%20a%20spacecraft%20designed%20for%20crew%20transport.%20However%2C%20their%20return%20was%20delayed%20due%20to%20a%20helium%20leak%20in%20the%20propulsion%20system%2C%20making%20re-entry%20unsafe.%20%E2%80%9CEntering%20and%20leaving%20Earth%20is%20very%20risky%2C%20and%20this%20spacecraft%20faced%20a%20helium%20leakage%2C%20so%20it%20could%20not%20leave%20the%20ISS%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Rachna.%20Eventu